Package com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.rmi

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IField
    Represents a FIX field and its value.
    IFixListener
    This interface defines the methods that are called on any listener to Fix.
    IMessageList
    Represents a list of messages.
    IProxy  
    IRemoteMessage
    This represents a FIX message exposed through RMI.
    IRemoteMessageFactory
    Used to create message related objects on the Catalys Server.
    IRmiApplication
    The Catalys Server application is represented by a remote object with this interface.
    ISession
    Represents a FIX session with a party.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PersistentFIXMessageBuffer
    Class which maintains a persistent buffer of IFIXMessages.
    RemoteConnectionEvent  
    RemoteExceptionEvent  
    RemoteMessageEvent  
    RemoteNotifier
    This is used to actually call back the remote IFixListener RMI objects.
    RemoteResetEvent  
    RmiAdapter
    This is a standard Catalys Server message processor which listens to incoming FIX messages and sends them out over RMI, and is a source of FIX messages received from external RMI applications.
    RmiApplication
    This singleton object represents the Application - ie the Catalys Server.
    RmiField  
    RmiMessage
    Standard Message object exposed through RMI.
    RmiMessageFactory  
    RmiMessageList  
    RmiSession
    RMI server object for servicing remote ISession requests from an RMI client.
